=Episode 36=

4
00:01:38,975 --> 00:01:39,734
Hello, Xiang Nan.

5
00:01:40,374 --> 00:01:41,175
Hey, Qian.

6
00:01:41,214 --> 00:01:42,734
We got out.

7
00:01:43,094 --> 00:01:44,255
Zhong is driving.

8
00:01:44,374 --> 00:01:45,055
We're on our way back.

9
00:01:46,014 --> 00:01:47,574
How are things on your end?

10
00:01:48,615 --> 00:01:50,775
I'll call you guys later.

11
00:01:51,415 --> 00:01:51,934
How did Mavis

12
00:01:51,934 --> 00:01:53,094
get hurt?

13
00:01:54,654 --> 00:01:55,535
Just tell her honestly,

14
00:01:55,654 --> 00:01:56,535
and take care of yourself.

15
00:01:56,535 --> 00:01:57,695
Alright, I know.

16
00:02:05,055 --> 00:02:06,374
That's all about it.

17
00:02:08,374 --> 00:02:09,214
Jiang Hongbin

18
00:02:09,255 --> 00:02:10,335
has character flaws.

19
00:02:11,335 --> 00:02:12,775
You've lived with him for so many years,

20
00:02:13,094 --> 00:02:14,415
so you should know better than I do.

21
00:02:15,854 --> 00:02:16,734
As you saw,

22
00:02:17,375 --> 00:02:19,095
Xiang Nan risked possibly

23
00:02:19,255 --> 00:02:20,854
getting hurt by Jiang Hongbin again

24
00:02:21,054 --> 00:02:22,215
to find Jiang Xiaotong.

25
00:02:23,734 --> 00:02:25,294
It wasn't just for her own sake.

26
00:02:26,375 --> 00:02:27,815
She's genuinely concerned about Xiaotong

27
00:02:28,774 --> 00:02:29,655
and hoped

28
00:02:29,774 --> 00:02:30,815
Xiaotong could see you

29
00:02:30,815 --> 00:02:31,774
in the video

30
00:02:32,454 --> 00:02:33,695
for some comfort.

31
00:02:34,495 --> 00:02:35,655
Can you bear to leave such a kind

32
00:02:35,734 --> 00:02:37,095
and brave daughter

33
00:02:38,375 --> 00:02:39,095
in the hands of someone

34
00:02:39,135 --> 00:02:40,294
like Jiang Hongbin?

35
00:02:41,334 --> 00:02:42,014
Yes,

36
00:02:43,255 --> 00:02:44,375
I came to Canada

37
00:02:44,375 --> 00:02:45,495
for my sister,

38
00:02:46,415 --> 00:02:47,255
but I believe

39
00:02:47,375 --> 00:02:49,014
I can also help your daughter and you.

40
00:02:52,975 --> 00:02:54,535
Shall we discuss more?

41
00:02:59,734 --> 00:03:00,535
Go ahead.

42
00:03:03,734 --> 00:03:05,215
You've returned there multiple times

43
00:03:05,655 --> 00:03:07,574
asking Jiang Hongbin for money.

44
00:03:09,655 --> 00:03:10,695
Do you have anything on him

45
00:03:10,815 --> 00:03:12,334
that could hold him accountable?

46
00:03:13,734 --> 00:03:14,655
If you do,

47
00:03:16,454 --> 00:03:17,975
I hope you can help us.

48
00:03:29,294 --> 00:03:30,255
Whether I have something

49
00:03:30,294 --> 00:03:32,174
that could hold
Jiang Hongbin accountable

50
00:03:33,014 --> 00:03:34,774
is none of your business.

51
00:03:36,135 --> 00:03:37,135
Even if I did,

52
00:03:37,935 --> 00:03:39,255
why would I give it to you?

53
00:03:40,014 --> 00:03:41,294
Do you think just

54
00:03:41,294 --> 00:03:42,255
by flying to Canada,

55
00:03:42,334 --> 00:03:44,535
throwing a fit in front of me,

56
00:03:44,854 --> 00:03:46,495
and I'll side with you

57
00:03:47,294 --> 00:03:48,535
and help you?

58
00:03:50,574 --> 00:03:51,815
You're too naive.

59
00:03:51,975 --> 00:03:53,215
Just go back.

60
00:03:54,375 --> 00:03:56,495
The Chinese community
here in Canada is small.

61
00:03:57,215 --> 00:03:59,495
I looked you up before I came.

62
00:04:00,454 --> 00:04:01,774
You're a person with no credibility

63
00:04:02,294 --> 00:04:04,095
and can't leave Canada.

64
00:04:05,655 --> 00:04:07,375
In your battle with Jiang Hongbin,

65
00:04:07,375 --> 00:04:08,014
you have already

66
00:04:08,054 --> 00:04:09,255
completely lost to him.

67
00:04:10,135 --> 00:04:11,215
If you still hope

68
00:04:11,255 --> 00:04:12,894
to get something from Jiang Hongbin,

69
00:04:15,294 --> 00:04:16,854
your only option may be through us.

70
00:04:17,255 --> 00:04:18,415
Through you?

71
00:04:20,294 --> 00:04:22,094
I want one hundred million.

72
00:04:22,534 --> 00:04:23,815
Can you give me?

73
00:04:27,295 --> 00:04:29,214
Jiang Hongbin is a very arrogant person.

74
00:04:30,695 --> 00:04:32,135
Before marrying Xiang Nan,

75
00:04:32,214 --> 00:04:33,774
he didn't sign a prenuptial agreement.

76
00:04:34,055 --> 00:04:35,574
Do you know what that means?

77
00:04:37,414 --> 00:04:38,815
I checked with a lawyer.

78
00:04:39,654 --> 00:04:41,654
If they divorce through litigation,

79
00:04:42,295 --> 00:04:43,615
Xiang Nan could get

80
00:04:43,774 --> 00:04:44,815
half of Jiang Hongbin's total income

81
00:04:45,295 --> 00:04:47,295
during their marriage,

82
00:04:47,815 --> 00:04:49,014
or even more.

83
00:04:51,295 --> 00:04:52,454
We don't want any of it.

84
00:04:53,935 --> 00:04:54,855
We'll give all of it to you.

85
00:05:07,135 --> 00:05:08,894
Jiang Hongbin didn't
just hurt Xiang Nan.

86
00:05:10,014 --> 00:05:11,454
He hurt my family,

87
00:05:13,495 --> 00:05:15,135
and someone

88
00:05:15,175 --> 00:05:16,654
incredibly important to me.

89
00:05:17,255 --> 00:05:18,214
I'm sure he's hurt

90
00:05:18,214 --> 00:05:19,534
you deeply too.

91
00:05:29,094 --> 00:05:30,695
You hate Jiang Hongbin,

92
00:05:33,815 --> 00:05:35,375
and I hate him even more.

93
00:05:36,735 --> 00:05:38,534
He reported my dual nationality,

94
00:05:38,735 --> 00:05:40,175
sending me back to Canada.

95
00:05:41,014 --> 00:05:42,695
He promised me money

96
00:05:42,815 --> 00:05:44,375
but only gave me a third of it.

97
00:05:45,214 --> 00:05:46,574
I was sued when I got back.

98
00:05:47,295 --> 00:05:48,214
I'm stuck

99
00:05:48,935 --> 00:05:50,454
in this godforsaken place,

100
00:05:52,574 --> 00:05:54,974
which is nothing different
from being imprisoned.

101
00:05:58,094 --> 00:05:59,014
But,

102
00:05:59,855 --> 00:06:01,135
no matter how terrible he is,

103
00:06:02,774 --> 00:06:04,574
he's still my daughter's father.

104
00:06:06,695 --> 00:06:07,495
I...

105
00:06:10,414 --> 00:06:11,375
I have no choice

106
00:06:11,414 --> 00:06:12,855
but to rely on him.

107
00:06:19,855 --> 00:06:20,574
Look,

108
00:06:22,094 --> 00:06:23,855
I can't even trust

109
00:06:24,175 --> 00:06:25,414
the closest people in my life.

110
00:06:26,175 --> 00:06:27,574
Why would I trust you,

111
00:06:27,774 --> 00:06:28,974
someone who has no relationship with me?

112
00:06:31,055 --> 00:06:32,214
What if you lose

113
00:06:32,214 --> 00:06:32,935
the divorce case?

114
00:06:33,175 --> 00:06:33,894
Well.

115
00:06:34,534 --> 00:06:35,695
Let's say you win the case.

116
00:06:36,094 --> 00:06:37,295
How do I know you won't back out

117
00:06:37,375 --> 00:06:38,615
and refuse to give me the money?

118
00:06:39,654 --> 00:06:40,974
I don't trust things

119
00:06:41,534 --> 00:06:42,815
that can't be seen.

120
00:06:44,414 --> 00:06:45,414
Who knows I will have

121
00:06:45,574 --> 00:06:47,375
to argue over this with you
across the Pacific?

122
00:06:48,815 --> 00:06:50,334
I don't have the energy.

123
00:06:52,615 --> 00:06:53,334
So,

124
00:06:55,855 --> 00:06:57,055
I can't help you.

125
00:06:58,375 --> 00:06:59,815
Don't come looking for me again,

126
00:06:59,974 --> 00:07:00,574
okay?

127
00:07:00,894 --> 00:07:02,295
Even if you come, I won't meet you.

128
00:07:03,695 --> 00:07:04,414
Ms. Li,

129
00:07:05,295 --> 00:07:06,414
send the guest off.

130
00:07:08,974 --> 00:07:09,735
Xu Sumin,

131
00:07:10,295 --> 00:07:11,375
if you can't pay back the money,

132
00:07:11,534 --> 00:07:13,055
you won't be able to leave Canada.

133
00:07:13,414 --> 00:07:14,574
Your daughter will remain

134
00:07:14,654 --> 00:07:15,935
under Jian Hongbin's control in China.

135
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:18,414
Do you think he'll ever let Xiaotong

136
00:07:18,495 --> 00:07:19,375
come back?

137
00:07:20,295 --> 00:07:20,894
Are you okay

138
00:07:20,935 --> 00:07:22,495
with never seeing your daughter again?

139
00:07:30,375 --> 00:07:31,375
Please leave.

140
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,440
(Jiang Hongbin)

141
00:08:13,894 --> 00:08:15,375
What's the matter? Speak.

142
00:08:16,695 --> 00:08:17,574
When are you going to give me

143
00:08:17,574 --> 00:08:19,094
the rest of the money?

144
00:08:20,055 --> 00:08:20,774
As soon as possible.

145
00:08:21,414 --> 00:08:22,815
How soon?

146
00:08:24,255 --> 00:08:25,815
Can you stop pushing me?

147
00:08:27,495 --> 00:08:28,534
You never intend

148
00:08:28,534 --> 00:08:29,935
to give it to me,

149
00:08:30,495 --> 00:08:31,135
right?

150
00:08:32,735 --> 00:08:34,214
It's not that I don't want to.

151
00:08:34,654 --> 00:08:35,534
It's that I really

152
00:08:35,615 --> 00:08:36,454
don't have that much right now.

153
00:08:36,894 --> 00:08:37,934
You're not going

154
00:08:38,975 --> 00:08:40,615
to give me the rest, right?

155
00:08:45,054 --> 00:08:45,774
Xu Sumin,

156
00:08:48,014 --> 00:08:49,615
are you asking for too much?

157
00:09:06,654 --> 00:09:07,255
Madam,

158
00:09:07,654 --> 00:09:09,014
the lady left a note

159
00:09:09,135 --> 00:09:10,654
on the door.

160
00:09:24,294 --> 00:09:26,294
(This is my hotel address
and contact number.)

161
00:09:27,054 --> 00:09:29,135
(I have a 180-day stay in Canada.)

162
00:09:29,975 --> 00:09:30,735
(Once you make up your mind,)

163
00:09:30,735 --> 00:09:31,814
(you can come find me anytime.)

164
00:09:33,375 --> 00:09:34,255
(If you couldn't make it this time,)

165
00:09:34,735 --> 00:09:35,975
(I will come back again next time.)

166
00:09:38,255 --> 00:09:39,894
(If we lose the divorce case,)

167
00:09:40,455 --> 00:09:41,255
(regarding the money,)

168
00:09:41,894 --> 00:09:43,534
(even if we have to sell
our house and car,)

169
00:09:44,135 --> 00:09:45,095
(we may not meet)

170
00:09:45,135 --> 00:09:46,294
(all your demands.)

171
00:09:47,294 --> 00:09:48,975
(But, it's still be
a significant sum of money.)

172
00:09:51,215 --> 00:09:52,135
(For the sake of Xiang Nan,)

173
00:09:52,575 --> 00:09:54,534
(my family will go all out.)

174
00:09:55,135 --> 00:09:56,654
(Even if there's only a slim chance,)

175
00:09:57,375 --> 00:09:59,054
(I'll fight for my family.)

176
00:10:19,294 --> 00:10:20,095
Ms. Li.

177
00:10:21,894 --> 00:10:22,774
Ms. Li!

178
00:10:24,735 --> 00:10:25,495
Madam.

179
00:10:29,455 --> 00:10:31,135
Tomorrow, please deliver
something for me

180
00:10:34,855 --> 00:10:35,774
to this address.

181
00:10:54,580 --> 00:11:00,540
(Arrivals)

182
00:11:19,934 --> 00:11:20,654
Attorney Wu,

183
00:11:20,735 --> 00:11:21,735
I currently have

184
00:11:21,814 --> 00:11:23,054
a very important document.

185
00:11:23,615 --> 00:11:24,654
If you're still awake,

186
00:11:24,735 --> 00:11:25,855
I can bring them to you right now.

187
00:11:25,855 --> 00:11:26,575
Is that okay?

188
00:12:28,455 --> 00:12:32,654
Happy birthday.

189
00:12:32,894 --> 00:12:35,894
♪Happy birthday to you♪

190
00:12:36,095 --> 00:12:39,455
♪Happy birthday to you♪

191
00:12:39,774 --> 00:12:43,335
♪Happy birthday to you♪

192
00:12:43,615 --> 00:12:46,215
Happy birthday, Mum.

193
00:12:46,215 --> 00:12:47,174
Come on.

194
00:12:47,215 --> 00:12:48,174
Mum.

195
00:12:49,774 --> 00:12:52,694
Mum, I love you the most.

196
00:12:53,014 --> 00:12:54,534
Mum, I wish you to stay young forever,

197
00:12:54,694 --> 00:12:56,215
always eighteen!

198
00:12:57,095 --> 00:12:57,575
Okay.

199
00:12:57,575 --> 00:12:58,575
I also wish for Mum

200
00:12:58,774 --> 00:13:00,934
to always stay with us,

201
00:13:01,014 --> 00:13:02,135
happy every day.

202
00:13:02,215 --> 00:13:02,774
Alright.

203
00:13:03,774 --> 00:13:04,414
Happy.

204
00:13:04,455 --> 00:13:05,934
Qian, come make a wish!

205
00:13:06,174 --> 00:13:06,694
Make a wish.

206
00:13:06,735 --> 00:13:07,455
Come on, hurry up!

207
00:13:07,575 --> 00:13:08,694
Make a wish!

208
00:13:09,095 --> 00:13:09,654
Thank you for all you do.

209
00:13:09,694 --> 00:13:10,774
Our family never celebrates birthdays.

210
00:13:11,135 --> 00:13:12,894
- We should celebrate it.
- That's right.

211
00:13:13,054 --> 00:13:15,095
Everyone has a chance
to change luck then.

212
00:13:15,735 --> 00:13:17,495
So, I'm the one
to change everyone's luck.

213
00:13:17,855 --> 00:13:18,814
You're right.

214
00:13:19,255 --> 00:13:20,294
We're using you to bring good fortune.

215
00:13:21,255 --> 00:13:21,735
Hurry up.

216
00:13:21,735 --> 00:13:22,694
Make a wish.

217
00:13:29,694 --> 00:13:31,294
I'm done. Let's blow the candle.

218
00:13:35,495 --> 00:13:39,014
Happy birthday.

219
00:13:39,735 --> 00:13:42,135
Shall we take a group photo?

220
00:13:42,255 --> 00:13:43,455
- Who's holding it?
- I'll do it.

221
00:13:44,294 --> 00:13:46,255
Come on.

222
00:13:46,615 --> 00:13:47,615
Come here.

223
00:13:47,814 --> 00:13:49,814
Three, two, one...

224
00:13:49,814 --> 00:13:51,135
Happy birthday!

225
00:13:51,294 --> 00:13:53,095
Happy birthday!

226
00:13:53,495 --> 00:13:54,534
I want to eat cake.

227
00:13:54,855 --> 00:13:57,135
You're having it now.

228
00:13:57,735 --> 00:13:59,294
You can't be that greedy.

229
00:13:59,575 --> 00:14:00,455
Here's the longevity noodles for you!

230
00:14:00,575 --> 00:14:01,215
Here you go!

231
00:14:01,455 --> 00:14:02,455
Here, Xiang Qian.

232
00:14:02,654 --> 00:14:03,215
Thank you, Dad.

233
00:14:03,255 --> 00:14:03,814
Here you go.

234
00:14:05,174 --> 00:14:06,414
Dad has never

235
00:14:06,495 --> 00:14:07,375
celebrated your birthday.

236
00:14:07,934 --> 00:14:09,054
Don't blame Dad.

237
00:14:09,335 --> 00:14:10,375
Happy birthday.

238
00:14:10,774 --> 00:14:11,534
Thank you, Dad.

239
00:14:12,735 --> 00:14:14,615
From now on,
whenever it's someone's birthday,

240
00:14:14,735 --> 00:14:15,894
we'll all gather

241
00:14:16,135 --> 00:14:17,135
to celebrate together.

242
00:14:17,774 --> 00:14:19,534
Remember what your dad said,

243
00:14:19,615 --> 00:14:20,455
otherwise he will forget it next year.

244
00:14:20,615 --> 00:14:22,335
The same goes for Cong and Qi.

245
00:14:22,455 --> 00:14:23,375
I want to have eggs too.

246
00:14:23,694 --> 00:14:25,174
- Sure!
- I want it too.

247
00:14:25,255 --> 00:14:26,654
Everyone will have it.

248
00:14:27,335 --> 00:14:28,375
Aren't you going to let us eat already?

249
00:14:28,375 --> 00:14:31,215
Everyone will have it.

250
00:14:32,215 --> 00:14:33,375
Come on.

251
00:14:34,774 --> 00:14:35,495
I'm digging in.

252
00:14:35,654 --> 00:14:36,375
How is it?

253
00:14:36,375 --> 00:14:37,174
Eat up.

254
00:14:38,934 --> 00:14:39,575
So delicious.

255
00:14:40,654 --> 00:14:41,054
Mum,

256
00:14:41,054 --> 00:14:42,495
isn't there a saying
that goes like this,

257
00:14:43,335 --> 00:14:45,054
"Dumplings before leaving,
noodles after coming back"?

258
00:14:46,575 --> 00:14:47,934
"Noodles after coming back,
dumplings before leaving"?

259
00:14:47,934 --> 00:14:49,615
Yes, you're right.

260
00:14:51,054 --> 00:14:52,774
I said it the other way round.

261
00:14:53,534 --> 00:14:55,135
It just so happened that I've returned.

262
00:14:56,135 --> 00:14:56,814
Before leaving...

263
00:14:57,135 --> 00:14:58,855
Eating dumplings before leaving

264
00:14:59,014 --> 00:15:01,014
denotes a smooth journey.

265
00:15:01,735 --> 00:15:02,975
And, eating noodles after coming back

266
00:15:02,975 --> 00:15:04,975
means you're staying longer,

267
00:15:05,014 --> 00:15:05,814
getting grounded here.

268
00:15:06,975 --> 00:15:08,615
Then, we still owe Qian a dumpling meal.

269
00:15:08,735 --> 00:15:09,174
You're right.

270
00:15:11,215 --> 00:15:11,934
I'm not leaving anymore.

271
00:15:12,294 --> 00:15:13,774
I want some too.

272
00:15:14,014 --> 00:15:15,414
I want some too.

273
00:15:15,654 --> 00:15:16,495
I want some too.

274
00:15:16,495 --> 00:15:17,135
Is there more?

275
00:15:17,294 --> 00:15:17,814
There is.

276
00:15:17,894 --> 00:15:18,934
I'll get a bowl for you.

277
00:15:19,095 --> 00:15:19,894
That's great.

278
00:15:19,934 --> 00:15:20,654
Do you want it too?

279
00:15:20,654 --> 00:15:21,294
Yeah, I can have some noodles!

280
00:15:21,294 --> 00:15:22,014
Anyone else want it?

281
00:15:22,694 --> 00:15:23,455
Me!

282
00:15:23,495 --> 00:15:24,335
Everyone will get it.

283
00:15:24,495 --> 00:15:25,375
I want to eat eggs.

284
00:15:26,054 --> 00:15:27,335
Everyone will get it.

285
00:15:27,455 --> 00:15:28,135
Come.

286
00:16:07,054 --> 00:16:08,735
How annoying!

287
00:16:11,135 --> 00:16:12,135
What's going on?

288
00:16:12,135 --> 00:16:13,095
Get up!

289
