00:31:02,654 --> 00:31:04,095
how popular your art piece is?

578
00:31:04,494 --> 00:31:05,335
Oh my goodness!

579
00:31:05,335 --> 00:31:06,174
Do you know that a few of us

580
00:31:06,214 --> 00:31:07,535
are in the studio working non-stop?

581
00:31:07,615 --> 00:31:09,254
Our eyes are practically going blind.

582
00:31:09,295 --> 00:31:10,535
Can't you have some sympathy for us?

583
00:31:10,615 --> 00:31:11,535
You've really worked hard for it.

584
00:31:11,575 --> 00:31:12,494
You're so heartless!

585
00:31:12,535 --> 00:31:13,654
Come on, take a seat.

586
00:31:14,214 --> 00:31:15,135
Whether you care about me or not,

587
00:31:15,174 --> 00:31:16,494
you should at least care
about your man, Lv Liang,

588
00:31:16,494 --> 00:31:17,375
okay?

589
00:31:18,855 --> 00:31:19,974
How's he doing?

590
00:31:20,694 --> 00:31:21,375
He's fine.

591
00:31:21,535 --> 00:31:23,295
Still in the 'workaholic' phase.

592
00:31:25,694 --> 00:31:26,454
When will he be back?

593
00:31:26,535 --> 00:31:27,775
I miss him.

594
00:31:28,414 --> 00:31:29,894
You talk every day on the phone.

595
00:31:29,934 --> 00:31:31,414
Isn't that enough?

596
00:31:32,135 --> 00:31:33,615
It's not the same
as seeing him in person.

597
00:31:34,494 --> 00:31:35,254
Here you go.

598
00:31:36,375 --> 00:31:37,654
I pass this ticket to you first.

599
00:31:38,454 --> 00:31:39,855
Xiaotong will be back
in Shanghai next week

600
00:31:39,894 --> 00:31:40,815
for a boxing match.

601
00:31:40,894 --> 00:31:42,615
This is a VIP ticket
she saved just for you.

602
00:31:43,095 --> 00:31:44,335
Such a good girl!

603
00:31:45,095 --> 00:31:46,135
We'll go together then

604
00:31:46,135 --> 00:31:47,174
to support her.

605
00:31:47,214 --> 00:31:47,734
Sure!

606
00:31:50,815 --> 00:31:51,894
How are you doing lately?

607
00:31:52,535 --> 00:31:54,615
I'm doing great, and busy with the shop.

608
00:31:55,375 --> 00:31:55,894
Oh yeah,

609
00:31:56,375 --> 00:31:58,055
I visited my brother last week.

610
00:32:02,654 --> 00:32:03,535
How is he?

611
00:32:04,414 --> 00:32:05,335
He's getting old,

612
00:32:05,694 --> 00:32:06,974
and his hair turns gray.

613
00:32:07,494 --> 00:32:09,375
But, he is in a good state.

614
00:32:11,055 --> 00:32:12,414
He told me something.

615
00:32:13,335 --> 00:32:14,214
He told me

616
00:32:14,335 --> 00:32:15,135
that my parents

617
00:32:15,535 --> 00:32:17,414
didn't actually die in a car accident.

618
00:32:19,174 --> 00:32:21,214
My dad used to hit my mum,

619
00:32:21,295 --> 00:32:22,535
and my mum can't take it anymore.

620
00:32:24,254 --> 00:32:25,135
One day,

621
00:32:25,775 --> 00:32:27,015
she got my dad drunk

622
00:32:27,654 --> 00:32:28,654
and turned on the gas.

623
00:32:35,254 --> 00:32:37,335
He hid it from me all these years,

624
00:32:37,855 --> 00:32:39,775
because he worried
that I couldn't take it.

625
00:32:44,494 --> 00:32:45,974
At least your brother

626
00:32:47,254 --> 00:32:48,295
genuinely cares for you.

627
00:32:49,734 --> 00:32:50,535
I know.

628
00:32:54,974 --> 00:32:55,615
How about you?

629
00:32:56,934 --> 00:32:57,934
Do you still resent him?

630
00:33:02,775 --> 00:33:03,894
To be honest,

631
00:33:04,535 --> 00:33:05,855
I don't even think about hating

632
00:33:05,934 --> 00:33:07,015
or not.

633
00:33:08,615 --> 00:33:10,295
Now, I just want

634
00:33:11,615 --> 00:33:13,174
to live my own life well,

635
00:33:13,414 --> 00:33:14,974
focus on my career,

636
00:33:15,615 --> 00:33:17,055
and take care of my family.

637
00:33:18,815 --> 00:33:19,734
I hope that all of us

638
00:33:19,775 --> 00:33:21,055
can keep moving forward.

639
00:33:23,295 --> 00:33:25,734
Well said. Moving forward.

640
00:33:44,055 --> 00:33:45,934
There'll be regular
checkups every month.

641
00:33:46,214 --> 00:33:48,055
Xiang Zhong is twelve weeks along now
and needs to create a pregnancy profile.

642
00:33:48,254 --> 00:33:49,214
After that,

643
00:33:49,335 --> 00:33:50,454
she'll have to do monthly checkups.

644
00:33:50,494 --> 00:33:50,934
Look.

645
00:33:50,934 --> 00:33:51,575
That's great.

646
00:33:52,654 --> 00:33:53,214
What is this?

647
00:33:53,214 --> 00:33:54,494
Xiang Zhiying is having fun.

648
00:33:54,815 --> 00:33:55,815
A postcard.

649
00:33:55,974 --> 00:33:56,694
Look.

650
00:33:57,694 --> 00:33:58,734
This is from Yichang.

651
00:33:59,335 --> 00:34:00,015
In Sichuan, right?

652
00:34:00,015 --> 00:34:01,414
This place looks pretty nice.

653
00:34:01,454 --> 00:34:02,295
What Sichuan?

654
00:34:02,295 --> 00:34:03,454
That's Yibin, right?

655
00:34:03,894 --> 00:34:05,174
Where is Yichang again, Dad?

656
00:34:06,135 --> 00:34:08,095
In Hubei, where the
Gezhouba Dam is located.

657
00:34:08,095 --> 00:34:08,494
Oh, you...

658
00:34:08,535 --> 00:34:09,295
Gezhouba Dam.

659
00:34:10,015 --> 00:34:10,775
That's right.

660
00:34:10,855 --> 00:34:12,615
Yibin is known for its wine.

661
00:34:15,055 --> 00:34:15,654
Alright.

662
00:34:15,654 --> 00:34:17,135
I didn't learn it well.

663
00:34:17,135 --> 00:34:18,055
My geography is poor.

664
00:34:18,095 --> 00:34:18,935
I'm not good at geography.

665
00:34:19,055 --> 00:34:19,694
Xiang Qian.

666
00:34:20,734 --> 00:34:22,975
Will Chai Jin have time to come over?

667
00:34:23,495 --> 00:34:24,575
I bought a coral grouper.

668
00:34:25,174 --> 00:34:26,294
Chai Jin went on
a business trip to Beijing.

669
00:34:26,374 --> 00:34:27,174
He's not back yet.

670
00:34:27,814 --> 00:34:28,455
He's just got freedom,

671
00:34:28,535 --> 00:34:29,654
and you let him go on a business trip?

672
00:34:30,294 --> 00:34:31,174
He's my leader.

673
00:34:31,174 --> 00:34:32,615
I have no control over him.

674
00:34:33,694 --> 00:34:34,254
When he returns,

675
00:34:34,575 --> 00:34:35,254
have him come over.

676
00:34:35,575 --> 00:34:36,254
He has helped our family

677
00:34:36,334 --> 00:34:37,334
so much,

678
00:34:37,654 --> 00:34:38,814
we should thank him.

679
00:34:39,095 --> 00:34:39,654
Tell him

680
00:34:40,294 --> 00:34:41,615
that I'll drink with him.

681
00:34:41,734 --> 00:34:42,254
Just let him come over.

682
00:34:44,734 --> 00:34:46,854
It should be him drinking with you.

683
00:34:48,055 --> 00:34:49,535
Can you please let me save some face?

684
00:34:49,774 --> 00:34:51,734
See, your daughter knows you well.

685
00:34:51,975 --> 00:34:52,694
Oh no!

686
00:34:55,095 --> 00:34:56,294
This girl is too much.

687
00:34:56,294 --> 00:34:57,174
She's really your daughter!

688
00:34:57,334 --> 00:34:58,174
For the coral grouper,

689
00:34:58,294 --> 00:34:59,374
I can eat too.

690
00:34:59,814 --> 00:35:00,654
What should I do now?

691
00:35:01,055 --> 00:35:02,615
You two are really...

692
00:35:03,015 --> 00:35:05,455
(Chai Jin: Safely landed, don't worry.)

693
00:35:08,334 --> 00:35:10,975
My dad said when you get back
from the business trip,

694
00:35:11,135 --> 00:35:12,294
come over for dinner at my home.

695
00:35:12,455 --> 00:35:14,015
He wants to have a drink-off with you.

696
00:35:19,095 --> 00:35:19,895
(Chai Jin: Yes, madam.)

697
00:35:21,975 --> 00:35:22,895
Do you need my help?

698
00:35:23,334 --> 00:35:24,095
No, no.

699
00:35:24,334 --> 00:35:26,575
I have to be diligent
in getting good food.

700
00:35:33,254 --> 00:35:33,774
Driver,

701
00:35:34,415 --> 00:35:35,495
could you please go a little faster?

702
00:35:44,055 --> 00:35:44,615
Wait.

703
00:35:44,615 --> 00:35:45,814
I still feel like eating something.

704
00:35:46,015 --> 00:35:46,935
Don't eat anymore, it's too late.

705
00:35:46,935 --> 00:35:47,734
Still awake?

706
00:35:48,015 --> 00:35:48,615
Who's this?

707
00:35:48,615 --> 00:35:49,455
Both of you haven't slept yet.

708
00:35:49,654 --> 00:35:51,214
You have a big room with a big bed,

709
00:35:51,415 --> 00:35:52,374
but coming here to squeeze with us.

710
00:35:52,615 --> 00:35:54,135
I'm here to chat
with the pregnant mummy.

711
00:35:55,495 --> 00:35:56,015
Zhong,

712
00:35:56,015 --> 00:35:57,174
when's your due date?

713
00:35:58,455 --> 00:36:00,254
It should be March 10th,

714
00:36:00,294 --> 00:36:00,854
next year.

715
00:36:01,455 --> 00:36:01,774
Zhong,

716
00:36:01,814 --> 00:36:03,935
have you ever thought

717
00:36:04,015 --> 00:36:05,055
about what would you do

718
00:36:05,055 --> 00:36:06,334
if one day Deng Haiyang

719
00:36:06,334 --> 00:36:07,214
reverted to his old ways?

720
00:36:07,774 --> 00:36:09,135
I really haven't thought about it.

721
00:36:09,374 --> 00:36:10,015
If it happens, it happens.

722
00:36:10,294 --> 00:36:11,455
I can't control it.

723
00:36:11,575 --> 00:36:12,814
As long as I'm happy.

724
00:36:14,334 --> 00:36:15,254
Now you sound

725
00:36:15,854 --> 00:36:17,135
both confident and carefree.

726
00:36:18,174 --> 00:36:18,935
I've completely

727
00:36:18,935 --> 00:36:19,935
made peace with myself.

728
00:36:20,095 --> 00:36:21,575
I completely accept myself.

729
00:36:22,214 --> 00:36:23,455
I feel like, right now,

730
00:36:24,015 --> 00:36:25,694
I can choose to be pregnant,

731
00:36:25,814 --> 00:36:26,734
I can choose

732
00:36:26,774 --> 00:36:27,814
a job I like,

733
00:36:27,854 --> 00:36:29,015
and I can choose

734
00:36:29,334 --> 00:36:30,734
to go where I want to go.

735
00:36:30,774 --> 00:36:32,895
In short, as long as

736
00:36:33,374 --> 00:36:35,214
we have a choice, we don't have
to be afraid of anything.

737
00:36:36,455 --> 00:36:37,374
Yeah, not afraid of anything.

738
00:36:37,814 --> 00:36:38,535
I tell you,

739
00:36:38,854 --> 00:36:40,415
Deng Haiyang is good.

740
00:36:40,495 --> 00:36:40,935
Yeah.

741
00:36:40,975 --> 00:36:41,654
But, no matter how,

742
00:36:41,694 --> 00:36:43,334
he just has a few quirks.

743
00:36:43,615 --> 00:36:45,254
You need to keep reminding him

744
00:36:45,455 --> 00:36:46,814
and make sure you don't do

745
00:36:47,214 --> 00:36:48,734
all the parenting alone.

746
00:36:49,015 --> 00:36:50,294
You have to let him help you

747
00:36:50,334 --> 00:36:50,935
with the kid.

748
00:36:51,254 --> 00:36:51,694
That's right.

749
00:36:51,774 --> 00:36:53,575
Whether he turns over a new leaf or not,

750
00:36:53,935 --> 00:36:55,615
I feel you should influence him.

751
00:36:55,975 --> 00:36:57,214
Alright, I'll

752
00:36:58,654 --> 00:36:59,455
educate him bit by bit.

753
00:36:59,654 --> 00:37:00,854
With you two,

754
00:37:00,895 --> 00:37:01,814
no matter what,

755
00:37:01,814 --> 00:37:02,935
Deng Haiyang

756
00:37:02,935 --> 00:37:03,895
doesn't want to leave you.

757
00:37:04,095 --> 00:37:04,615
That's right.

758
00:37:04,935 --> 00:37:05,654
If he doesn't change himself,

759
00:37:05,694 --> 00:37:06,615
I wouldn't want to stay either.

760
00:37:06,935 --> 00:37:07,455
That's right.

761
00:37:08,055 --> 00:37:09,374
Having kids later

762
00:37:09,374 --> 00:37:10,214
is another chapter,

763
00:37:10,254 --> 00:37:11,895
and new problems might arise.

764
00:37:12,895 --> 00:37:13,535
Yes.

765
00:37:14,135 --> 00:37:15,854
Just think of him like a kid.

766
00:37:15,895 --> 00:37:16,495
Deng Haiyang

767
00:37:16,495 --> 00:37:17,535
is like a kid.

768
00:37:17,895 --> 00:37:18,495
You need

769
00:37:18,495 --> 00:37:19,455
to educate him too.

770
00:37:19,654 --> 00:37:20,174
Oh my goodness.

771
00:37:20,294 --> 00:37:21,575
It's like having two kids at home now.

772
00:37:21,814 --> 00:37:23,055
Look at our mum and dad.

773
00:37:23,174 --> 00:37:23,854
On the surface,

774
00:37:23,895 --> 00:37:25,015
it looks like Dad is pampering Mum,

775
00:37:25,174 --> 00:37:25,975
but actually,

776
00:37:25,975 --> 00:37:26,935
Mum is the one giving in to him.

777
00:37:26,935 --> 00:37:27,495
That's true.

778
00:37:27,495 --> 00:37:30,455
She just let him feel like
he's pampering her,

779
00:37:31,374 --> 00:37:31,895
right?

780
00:37:32,015 --> 00:37:33,135
Our mum is wise.

781
00:37:33,495 --> 00:37:34,095
You're right.

782
00:37:34,334 --> 00:37:35,455
Who left these three cards here?

783
00:37:35,535 --> 00:37:36,455
Here, this is for you.

784
00:37:36,895 --> 00:37:37,774
"Go to bed early, and get up early".

785
00:37:39,174 --> 00:37:39,895
Who left this here?

786
00:37:40,135 --> 00:37:41,095
I really go to bed early,
and get up early recently.

787
00:37:41,095 --> 00:37:42,095
"Life is like an ocean.",
here's one for you.

788
00:37:42,214 --> 00:37:43,694
"Life is like an ocean"?

789
00:37:43,935 --> 00:37:45,415
You've still got
a long journey ahead of you.

790
00:37:45,455 --> 00:37:46,415
Mine is "hahaha".

791
00:37:47,842 --> 00:37:51,070
♪How much love and hate fade away♪

792
00:37:51,271 --> 00:37:53,974
♪Spring goes and comes again♪

793
00:37:54,908 --> 00:37:58,158
♪So many grievances linger♪

794
00:37:58,325 --> 00:38:01,181
♪Wandering within time♪

795
00:38:02,042 --> 00:38:04,713
♪Unintentional forgetfulness♪

796
00:38:05,627 --> 00:38:08,337
♪Grows wildly without restraint♪

797
00:38:09,098 --> 00:38:12,722
♪Growing within growth,
staying silent within silence♪

798
00:38:12,796 --> 00:38:15,120
♪All will gather strength♪

799
00:38:15,121 --> 00:38:16,052
(The Following Spring)

800
00:38:16,054 --> 00:38:19,520
♪Time flows within memories♪

801
00:38:19,694 --> 00:38:20,455
Haiyang,

802
00:38:21,055 --> 00:38:22,055
household registration booklet, ID card,

803
00:38:22,135 --> 00:38:22,895
and birth permit,

804
00:38:23,015 --> 00:38:23,975
did you bring everything?

805
00:38:24,174 --> 00:38:25,334
Yes, yes.

806
00:38:25,535 --> 00:38:25,975
I've got everything.

807
00:38:25,975 --> 00:38:26,774
You have to check carefully.

808
00:38:26,774 --> 00:38:27,334
I tell you,

809
00:38:27,334 --> 00:38:28,294
after the child is born,

810
00:38:28,535 --> 00:38:29,774
you'll need all of them
for the birth certificate.

811
00:38:29,975 --> 00:38:31,214
You can't miss even one thing.

812
00:38:31,415 --> 00:38:31,895
Don't worry.

813
00:38:31,895 --> 00:38:32,654
I checked

814
00:38:32,734 --> 00:38:33,615
over eighty times last night.

815
00:38:33,654 --> 00:38:34,615
Nothing's missing.

816
00:38:34,694 --> 00:38:35,214
Here, here.

817
00:38:35,294 --> 00:38:36,174
I'll carry it.

818
00:38:36,174 --> 00:38:36,975
You stay at home.

819
00:38:37,254 --> 00:38:38,055
The car can't accommodate more.

820
00:38:38,135 --> 00:38:38,975
I'll lend a hand.

821
00:38:40,495 --> 00:38:41,214
Xiang Qian,

822
00:38:41,814 --> 00:38:42,814
are you going to the hospital too?

823
00:38:43,015 --> 00:38:43,575
Yes, I'm going.

824
00:38:43,814 --> 00:38:44,575
That's great then.

825
00:38:44,615 --> 00:38:45,374
If you didn't go,

826
00:38:45,774 --> 00:38:46,975
we couldn't rest assured.

827
00:38:47,055 --> 00:38:47,975
That's great.

828
00:38:47,975 --> 00:38:48,415
I'll go. I'll go.

829
00:38:48,455 --> 00:38:49,135
We both will be there.

830
00:38:49,254 --> 00:38:49,895
Great!

831
00:38:50,174 --> 00:38:52,015
Have you taken the maternity bag?

832
00:38:52,334 --> 00:38:53,694
Mum, it's over here!

833
00:38:53,694 --> 00:38:54,374
We got it all.

834
00:38:54,374 --> 00:38:55,095
Check again carefully

835
00:38:55,254 --> 00:38:56,214
to see if anything is missed.

836
00:38:56,214 --> 00:38:57,694
So, you don't have to rush
back later for anything.

837
00:38:57,734 --> 00:38:58,734
It's fine if they miss anything,

838
00:38:58,734 --> 00:38:59,654
I'll just come back to take it.

839
00:38:59,694 --> 00:39:00,694
Alright then.

840
00:39:02,814 --> 00:39:03,774
Where's my wife?

841
00:39:04,095 --> 00:39:05,174
Oh yeah!

842
00:39:05,615 --> 00:39:06,254
Oh right!

843
00:39:06,935 --> 00:39:07,935
We're all busy here.

844
00:39:08,174 --> 00:39:09,214
You guys forgot me huh?

845
00:39:09,495 --> 00:39:10,734
Oh my goodness!

846
00:39:11,055 --> 00:39:11,895
Sorry, sorry.

847
00:39:12,135 --> 00:39:14,455
We forgot the most important person.

848
00:39:14,654 --> 00:39:15,415
Hey,

849
00:39:15,495 --> 00:39:16,854
what were you doing?

850
00:39:18,174 --> 00:39:19,095
Be careful.

851
00:39:19,455 --> 00:39:20,135
I'm so clumsy now.

852
00:39:20,254 --> 00:39:21,135
Here you go.

853
00:39:22,654 --> 00:39:23,495
Be careful.

854
00:39:23,615 --> 00:39:24,495
When I delivered Xiang Zhong back then,

855
00:39:24,495 --> 00:39:25,615
I brought along Xiang Qian's

856
00:39:25,694 --> 00:39:26,935
auspicious lock charm with me.

857
00:39:27,254 --> 00:39:28,174
I'll go get it and put it on her.

858
00:39:28,334 --> 00:39:29,095
That's alright.

